## When to use this component

Use the tag component to indicate the status of something, such as an item on a [task list](../../patterns/task-list-pages) or a [phase banner](../phase-banner).

## How it works

There are 2 ways to use the tag component. You can use HTML or, if you are using [Nunjucks](https://mozilla.github.io/nunjucks/) or the [GOV.UK Prototype Kit](https://5e26c8c76425973408fe3240--govuk-prototype-kit-docs.netlify.com/), you can use the Nunjucks macro.

